The atitle command equips or clears an achievement title that you have
already unlocked.

Syntax:

  atitle
  atitle <title-id>
  atitle clear

Examples:

  atitle slayer:bronze
  atitle resurrectionist:gold
  atitle clear

To see the exact ids you can use, run:

  achievements titles

To see the overall achievement rankings, run:

  leaderboard

See also: help achievements, help achievement_titles
